at0000.1.description: A generic section header which should be renamed in a template to suit a specific clinical context.
Series of questions and associated answers used to screen for issues, problems or diagnoses.

at0028.1.text: Saya tidak mengerti bagaimana mengelola diabetes dengan regimen pengobatan saat ini
at0028.1.description: Is there a history of any issues, problems or diagnoses relevant for the screening purpose?
at0028.1.comment: In a template, the data element would usually be renamed to the specific question asked. The proposed value set can be adapted for local use by using the DV_TEXT or the DV_BOOLEAN datatypes choice to match each specific use case.

at0028.3.comment: In a template, the data element would usually be renamed to the specific question asked. The proposed value set can be adapted for local use by using the DV_TEXT or the DV_BOOLEAN datatypes choice to match each specific use case.

at0028.4.text: Saya merasa kelelahan karena berusaha menjaga kadar gula darah saya agar tetap sesuai target sepanjang waktu
